import React from 'react'
import {Grid} from '@mui/material'

const Profil = () => {

    return (
        <>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid md={5} sm={12}>

                </Grid>
                <Grid md={5} sm={12}>

                </Grid>
                <Grid md={2} sm={12}>
                    I
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid md={6} sm={12}>

                </Grid>
                <Grid md={6} sm={12}>

                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </>
    )
}

export default Profil
